title: Tierra Sana
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Bolivian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a healthier approach to multicultural cuisine. Has salads, soups, quiches, sandwiches, curry, stir fry, and desserts. Vegetarian except for chicken and fish. Cozy place, next to Oliver's Travels British pub.
